sp_scores.title: Exploit the Heli Gunner's weakness to lighting attacks.

tip_battle.message: Melee attacks won't reach the Heli Gunner, kupo! Use lightning and ranged attacks instead!
tip_battle.title: Heli Gunner

sp_scores.title: Defeat Bottomswell without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Melee attacks can't reach Bottomswell, kupo, so plan ahead! If someone gets trapped in a Water Cell, your other party members will have to use magic attacks to break them out! Trapped characters take damage, so target them to get them out fast!
tip_battle.title: Bottomswell

sp_scores.title: Exploit the Proudclad's weakness to lightning attacks.
Defeat the Proudclad without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: The Proudclad is a powerful enemy with no elemental weaknesses, kupo! But once you defeat the Jamar Armor on its chest, it becomes vulnerable to lightning! Take out the Jamar Armor first, then lower its Resistance with Mental Break and take it out fast, blitz style!
tip_battle.title: Proudclad

sp_scores.title: Defeat Schizo without being KO'd.
Win without Tifa being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Schizo has two targets, kupo, its white right head and its red left head! The white head absorbs fire, and the red head absorbs ice, so be careful! Focus your attacks to bring down one of the heads fast!
tip_battle.title: Schizo

sp_scores.title: Defeat the Dragon without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: The Dragon has group attacks and powerful single-target attacks, kupo. If you can inflict it with Paralyze or Blind, the battle will be much easier! It absorbs fire damage, so stay away from that!
tip_battle.title: Dragon

sp_scores.title: Exploit the Hundred Gunner's weakness to lightning attacks.

tip_battle.message: Melee attacks won't reach the Hundred Gunner, kupo! When it gets low on HP, it starts using extra powerful attacks, so try to take it down quick with lightning and ranged attacks!
tip_battle.title: Hundred Gunner

sp_scores.title: Defeat Blood Taste without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Blood Taste may not have elemental weaknesses, but debuffs will work, kupo! Use Sleep, Paralyze, Blind, and other debuffs to give this beast a taste of its own blood!
tip_battle.title: Blood Taste

sp_scores.title: Defeat the Dragon without being KO'd.

tip_battle.title: Dragon

sp_scores.title: Defeat Rapps without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Rapps mostly uses physical attacks like Scorpion's Tail, kupo! If you can Blind it, the fight will be much easier!
tip_battle.title: Rapps

sp_scores.title: Defeat Gi Nattak without being KO'd.
Exploit Gi Nattak's weakness to holy attacks.

tip_battle.message: Gi Nattak is vulnerable to holy attacks, and Soul Fire is vulnerable to holy and wind attacks, kupo! Soul Fire can possess your characters, and if it does, it will use Fira to chip away at their HP. You can't avoid being possessed, but you can be ready for the fire damage!
tip_battle.title: Gi Nattak & Soul Fire
